HELP SIMPLE_READ                                        Steve Knight, Nov 93
                                                        SIREN Project
lib simple_read

This library provides a collection of procedures for reading items from
*PROGLIST.

    read_token() -> ITEM
    read_word() -> WORD
    read_number() -> ITEM
    drop_token()
    peek_token() -> ITEM
    can_read( ITEM | ITEMLIST ) -> ITEM | FALSE
    must_read( ITEM | ITEMLIST ) -> ITEM


